subject: Bicycles and Bicycling
Tour de France (Bicycle Race)
Doping (Sports)
lead_paragraph: Lance Armstrong will return to professional cycling in late January in Australia, as planned, nearly two weeks before he is eligible to race under anti-doping rules.
